1. *Zahvaljujem* se na pozivu. (I thank you for the invitation.)
2. Želim da se *zahvalim* svima koji su mi pomogli. (I want to thank everyone who helped me.)
3. Oni će *zahvaliti* profesoru na njegovoj podršci. (They will thank the professor for his support.)
4. *Zahvaljivanje* na uspehu je važno za motivaciju. (Expressing gratitude for success is important for motivation.)
5. Nisam uspeo da mu se *zahvalim* na vremenu koje mi je posvetio. (I didn't manage to thank him for the time he dedicated to me.)
6. Molim vas da mi *zahvalite* na njihovom trudu. (Please thank them on my behalf for their efforts.)
7. Kada si mu *zahvalio* na poklonu? (When did you thank him for the gift?)
8. Moramo se *zahvaliti* na ovom divnom danu. (We have to give thanks for this beautiful day.)
9. Ona je izgubila priliku da im se *zahvali* na gostoprimstvu. (She missed the chance to thank them for their hospitality.)
10. *Zahvalnost* je važna vrlina koju treba razvijati. (Gratitude is an important virtue that should be cultivated.)